high_descs: Turn around, move around the island to the right, head to the sink, turn left to face the cabinet right of the stove.
Open up the cabinet over the counter and pick up the plate in there.
Bring the plate over to the microwave on the left, over the stove.
Heat the plate in the microwave.
Take the heated plate over to the sink on the right.
Put the heated plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated plate in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and then right to find the counter, and look up.
Open the top cabinet to the right and take out a plate.
Carry the plate and move a step to the left.q
Place the plate in the microwave above, then shut the door. Open the door and take the plate out.
Take the plate and turn to the right and find the sink.
Place the plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Heat a plate and place it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the opening between the kitchen counter and the island, turn right and go to the last cabinet, on the top, left side of the kitchen.
Pull a plate out from the right side of the cupboard.
Go to the microwave, above the stove, to your left.
Place the plate in the microwave, heat it up, and remove the plate from the microwave.
Turn to your right and go to the sink.
Place the plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm plate in the kitchen sink.
